  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <p>
      Our design principles are shared guidelines that capture the essence of what good design means our company and
      advice on how to achieve it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked sprk-o-Flag--middle">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="120" viewBox="0 0 246.21 219.77">
