        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Clarity
        </h2>
        <p>
          Help eliminate ambiguity and enable users to see, understand and act with confidence. Keep the user focused on
          their goal without distraction.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked sprk-o-Flag--middle">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="120" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
          <use xlink:href="#leaf" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Consistency
        </h2>
        <p>
          Create familiarity &amp; strengthen intuition by applying the same solution to the same problem. Use consistent
            language, patterns and components across the experience to make it easier for clients to get stuff done.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked sprk-o-Flag--middle">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="120" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
          <use xlink:href="#leaf" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Beauty
        </h2>
        <p>
          Every aesthetic design decision - from how we design components, to illustrations, and choices about color -
          should be purposeful. Build trust and further imbue confidence with an experience that appears and interacts
          beautifully.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked sprk-o-Flag--middle">
      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__figure">
        <svg height="120" viewBox="0 0 220.63 197.62">
