        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="sprk-o-Flag__body">
        <h2 class="drizzle-b-h2">
          Inclusive
        </h2>
        <p>
          Be inclusive, legible and as readable as possible across the experience. Thoughtfully serve the needs of all
          people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
    <div class="sprk-o-Flag sprk-o-Flag--stacked sprk-o-Flag--middle">
